&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Vice President People Experience&lt;/strong&gt; provides strategic and operational leadership across the People Experience function, ensuring people strategies, programs, and practices enable business success and an exceptional employee experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to help lead the next phase of integration between Gore Insurance Company, Unica Insurance, and Beneva. As part of a growing, purpose-driven mutual insurer, you will play a key role in shaping how teams, leaders, and employees come together to support a unified vision for the future while preserving the strengths and heritage of each organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Chief People Officer &amp;nbsp;this role serves as a trusted advisor on talent, culture, and organizational effectiveness while&lt;strong&gt; leading a multi-disciplinary HR team responsible for HR Business Partners, Talent Acquisition, People Operations, Total Rewards, and HR Policy.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As Gore and Unica continue their integration under the Beneva brand,&lt;/strong&gt; the Vice President will help align people strategies, strengthen organizational capability, and support employees through a period of meaningful growth and transformation. The combined organization brings greater scale, financial strength, and opportunities for continued investment in people, technology, and customer experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
