&lt;li&gt;Lead and develop a People Experience team of 15+ employees across HR Business Partners, Talent Acquisition, People Operations, and Total Rewards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute people strategies that support organizational priorities and business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with executives, people leaders, and the Board of Directors on workforce planning, organizational effectiveness, employee relations, and talent strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a high-performance, inclusive culture built on accountability, collaboration, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage people analytics and insights to support informed decision-making and measure organizational outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure HR programs, policies, and practices are aligned, effective, and scalable.&lt;/li&gt;
